post_text:
MISD Parents: please remember to complete the Free and Reduced Meal Application online...
https://www.myschoolapps.com/Home/PickDistrict

If you received a letter in the mail over the summer, please do not reapply for benefits. If you need to add children to the program, a new application must be submitted.

All Pre-K students qualify for free meals regardless of income. The cut-off date for temporary applications or carryover applications from the 2018-2019 school year will end on September 25, 2019. Please contact the Nutrition Department (254-840-2665 or carpenter@mcgregor-isd.org) with any questions.
